{"id": "1510693223973257256", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "分為混海和海超\n兩種配隊的打法和要求都不一樣", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T17:15:31.918000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510693739138519274", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "# 混海特性", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T17:17:34.743000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510693958081183754", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "打法是那種傳統深海\n隊伍要刷精通", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T17:18:26.943000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510695184881422516", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過\n2000血 400精通=320靜海盾\n2500血 200精通=300靜海盾\n所以我認為在有一定的精通情況下\n高血量>精通", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T17:23:19.435000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510695421901672632", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "因此 隊友的選擇可以先專注於高體質的\n畢竟+12凱就自帶36精通了", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T17:24:15.945000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510697625798705264", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "以下是一些混沌跟深海的體質以及某些人格深化的數據\n60級->70級\n\n常駐:\n\n諾締拉 152->171\n4.8強效 24精通\n+12：14.4強效 72精通\n\n拉蒙娜 120->135\n12精通\n+12：36精通\n\n潘 120->135\n\n法洛思 96->108\n9.6強效 12精通\n+12：28.8強效 36精通\n\n朵爾 88->99", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T17:33:01.395000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510701460109918309", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "限定:\n\n萊克 180->200\n\n莉莉 162->180\n9.6強效\n+12：28.8強效\n\n克珀珊特 144->160\n\n哈姆林 135->150\n\n墨菲 131->145", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T17:48:15.566000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
