{"id": "1510702578009247894", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "簡單來說就是一銀鑰位  一虛弱位", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T17:52:42.094000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510703873680080946", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "銀鑰位基本上有一套刷得好的生機榨取就可以\n所以我們可以先在上面找有虛弱的喚醒體\n墨菲>克珀珊特≥朵爾", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T17:57:51.006000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-31T18:53:24.682000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510704345597874236", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "我是建議看哪個不會用到就上哪個\n因此選一個虛弱位就可以撿垃圾了\n優先選有高體質或是同時有精通的", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T17:59:43.520000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
