{"id": "1510712134458413288", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "短暫的話是點凱\n有萊克的話可以考慮巨人", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T18:30:40.529000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510712225596440707", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "# 打法", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T18:31:02.258000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510713843515654306", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "-# 十分簡單\n記得在敵方打多段的時候開凱3算就差不多了\n\n覺醒安排：\n道中先覺凱 精英可以考慮二覺\n王關能多覺就多覺一點 可以在第6~8回考慮開第三覺醒\n也可以在最終爆發前覺醒", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T18:37:28+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-05-31T19:00:25.402000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510714553691017457", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "打法簡單來說就是凱單核\n在覺醒之後盡量多打他的牌 號令觸手攻擊累積反擊\n#   不要在回合開始就先開靜海\n請在輸出完之後缺盾再考慮", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T18:40:17.319000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510715077810983113", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "我建議從第二關道中開始就先開凱超限 (所以記得做狂氣狀態)\n那樣基本上就不會吃到凝視了", "timestamp": "2026-05-31T18:42:22.279000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
